      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-question">
          <span>What are rearing protocols?</span>
          <svg class="faq-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.293 7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Rearing protocols are structured developmental programs for puppies and other young animals. They include exercises, socialization activities, and handling routines designed to produce well-adjusted, confident animals. Examples include Early Neurological Stimulation (ENS), Early Scent Introduction (ESI), and the Rule of 7s.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-question">
          <span>What benchmark protocols are included?</span>
          <svg class="faq-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.293 7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>BreederHQ includes industry-standard protocols like ENS (Early Neurological Stimulation/Bio-Sensor Program), ESI (Early Scent Introduction), Rule of 7s, Puppy Culture exercises, and Avidog protocols. Each comes with day-by-day tasks, timing guidelines, and completion tracking.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-question">
          <span>Can I create my own custom protocols?</span>
          <svg class="faq-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.293 7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Yes. The Protocol Builder lets you create custom protocols with your own phases, tasks, and timing. You can start from scratch or modify existing protocols to match your program's approach.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

